comments.comment: Camera position is saved when a new issue is created.
Other users can comment on an issue later.
And continue the conversation anytime, anywhere.
Position of a clipping plane is also saved with the issue.
Clipping plane can be switched on/off in Clip card.
Click on the Clip button on the left edge of the screen to open the card.
Sample project is provided by Rob Jackson from Bond Bryan.
Camera position is saved when a new issue is created.
Other users can comment on an issue later.
Pin can be placed to highlight an element in the model.
Pin is saved with the issue an stays always visible.
Clicking on the pin opens the issue with saved view.
You can also sketch using the Scribble tool.
Sketches and markups are saved with the issue as well.
Use Erase tool to correct your sketch.
